The purpose of this code is to showcase my knowledge of various aspects of the C++ language.
The language features I use are:
(X) operator overloading
(X) Classes
(X) Inherited Classes
(X) Abstract Classes
( ) Smart Pointers
(X) Interacting with a SQLite DB
(X) Priority Queue
(X) Templates
(X) Map
(X) Vector
( ) Function Pointer
( ) SDL
( ) Valgrind For Memory Validating
( ) Error Handling
( ) Dynamically Allocating Memory


