Done:
operator overloading : overloading the << operator for nurses, patients.
classes : several classes
inherited classes : person -> nurse -> nurseXX
                    person -> patient
                    person -> doctor
abstract class : person
sqldb : use sqlite to get patient, nurse info.
priority queue : each nurse stores a priority queue of patients and pops one off, deciding where the nurse should go.
templates : the print_vector function is templated to print out the contents of arbitray vectors. Of course, the range based loop with auto would also work.
map: map storing the disease information
vector: all patients and nurses are stored in vectors.
